i beg you please help me !!{p}
i need to find out either the name of this game or find the game itself,
the only problem is that i cant remember what it is called, personally
I've never played it before but my brother has and he wont stop hassling
me to find it, so im passing the buck onto you guys!!, ha ha ha im free
I'm free  !!!!!.....get a grip,{p}
Any way the game is a fully renderd version of 3d tank that shot bouncing
fire balls at little spaceships that poped out of the ground wich also fired
fire balls at you, and there was a radar in the middle of the playing field in
which you had to fight for your life, the object of the game was to shoot
as many of the little silver ships as possable and then at the end there was
a double ended cone that had a doughnut in the middle of it wich shot the
hell out of you with fire balls.{p}
The game (He thinks) was released just after the Amiga 500 was
released.{p}
My brother remembers that a mate of his at the time had just bought an
Amiga 500, after a few months one of his mates had broght round a pile
of games from a games shop that he worked in at the time and gave him
the game that i am trying to find out about now.{p}
We think that the game might of been deleted about 4 maybe 5 years ago,
I'm not 100% about that though?, anyway i would be most greatfull if you
could shed any light on this as it is driving me nutts (Very Very Very
BIG understatement).{p}
E mail: {bold}sheila16@supanet.com{nobold}{p}
Thankyou,Thankyou and once again I thankyou......
