From : {bold}Barry Riddiford{nobold} <->
{p} {p}
Well this is a sad day for all of us! Anyone who keeps an eye out on
the usual Amiga sites won't fail to notice the letter to the Amiga
community from Ben Vost. Amiga Format is closing. For me, I've been
with the mag since at least 1992, it's come as a terrific blow. I
can't help but think the worst. I will be subscribing to AmigActive
but it's possibly too little too late. I urge all of you to do the
same cos this is the last magazine we have. I'm not including Clubbed
(by SEAL) or Amiga Survivor, both of which are brilliant magazines
but they don't have the financial clout. Anyway I'll sign off now cos
I'm going to dig out all my old mags and reminisce.
{p} {p}
Bazza
{p} {p}
